Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.10,0:00:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼要哭？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.89,0:00:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.46,0:00:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.16,0:00:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣看起來豈不像是我在單方面地欺負後輩嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.48,0:00:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想哭的是我才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.60,0:00:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但被妹妹敬而遠之 而且連個理由都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.30,0:00:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼不對我訴說呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.46,0:00:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你來說我就只是這種程度的人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.90,0:00:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 成為姐妹又有甚麼意義呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.30,0:00:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼你要接受念珠呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.63,0:00:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.90,0:00:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另找一天心平氣和地再談談吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.28,0:00:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也稍微有點過於激動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.71,0:01:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能說得也太過份了一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.11,0:01:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.39,0:01:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？ 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.22,0:01:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.93,0:01:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始商議明天活動吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.37,0:01:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒甚麼…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.37,0:01:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.27,0:01:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也想單方面地將我當成壞人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.85,0:01:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.19,0:01:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.18,0:01:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚集在瑪莉亞的庭院裡的少女們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.81,0:01:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也帶著天使般無垢的笑容 穿越與身同高的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.18,0:01:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覆蓋住純潔身心的是深色的制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.79,0:01:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓裙子的摺痕亂掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.67,0:02:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓白色的水手服領結外翻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.81,0:02:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒緩的行走成了這裡的習俗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.71,0:02:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私立莉莉安女學園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.32,0:02:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是少女的花園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.37,0:03:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)}吃驚的巧克力·後篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.24,0:03:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅薔薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.20,0:03:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是四季常開呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.45,0:04:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大概被姐姐討厭了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.14,0:04:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.84,0:04:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白薔薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.45,0:04:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我想你或許願意自已一個人待著 但…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.73,0:04:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過說起來 剛才真像是過去情景的重現啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.93,0:04:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.03,0:04:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳與祥子有時真是相似得讓人吃驚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.10,0:04:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的祐巳與祥子\N就像是一年又十個月以前的祥子與蓉子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.59,0:04:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是現在的紅薔薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.51,0:04:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子因為成長環境的原因 所以不大擅長表達自已的意見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.23,0:05:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經常因悶得慌而發脾氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.43,0:05:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是祥子大人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.06,0:05:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以某一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.43,0:05:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓉子對她訓斥道「你這樣我甚麼都無法明白」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.86,0:05:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「有想說的話就清楚地說出來」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.59,0:05:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼不說話？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.92,0:05:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你內心深處的話語為甚麼就不能向我傾訴？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.28,0:05:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話我甚麼都無法明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.68,0:05:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被蓉子那樣訓斥後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.61,0:05:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子也像是忍耐到了極限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.19,0:05:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後就漸漸變得能表達自已的意見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.60,0:05:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 這大概就是祥子對祐巳感到焦躁不安的原因吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.30,0:05:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焦躁不安？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.55,0:05:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.74,0:05:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.65,0:05:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.05,0:05:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為看到祐巳就像是看到了自已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.69,0:05:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子她的本性並未改變啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.71,0:05:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也一定是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.99,0:05:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才焦躁不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.37,0:06:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為在祐巳的身上\N看到了自已身上也有的討厭部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.53,0:06:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以原諒祥子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.75,0:06:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原諒甚麼的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.84,0:06:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 不要因為這點事就變得討厭祥子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.48,0:06:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.97,0:06:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.68,0:06:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對這個溫室 稍微有點過敏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.62,0:06:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.07,0:06:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白薔薇大人很快就要畢業了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.82,0:06:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後我該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.15,0:06:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再沒有能像這樣來幫助我的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.57,0:06:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是說了些讓人開心的話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.92,0:06:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總會有辦法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.14,0:06:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能再多向祥子訴說一些真心話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.43,0:06:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衹要至少能做到一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.77,0:06:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管發生甚麼事一定都能順利地渡過的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.38,0:07:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.80,0:07:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 向祐巳佈置一道作業題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.93,0:07:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑自已的力量與祥子重歸於好 好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.56,0:07:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.63,0:07:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～ 祐巳不送我巧克力嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.34,0:07:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向志摩子同學說聲「給我巧克力」不就好了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.58,0:07:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.65,0:07:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼只有放棄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.06,0:07:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.08,0:07:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不給我巧克力的話 我就吃掉祐巳喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.16,0:07:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊是祥子大人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.57,0:07:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗品就留作用情不專的白薔薇大人的懲罰用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.96,0:07:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是情人節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.13,0:07:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先必須對昨天的事道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.68,0:07:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 將祥子大人叫出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.11,0:08:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.79,0:08:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是祐巳同學啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.99,0:08:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志摩子同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.28,0:08:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人來了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.70,0:08:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 在上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.22,0:08:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.85,0:08:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.69,0:08:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.79,0:08:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志摩子同學也許把卡片藏在這裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.97,0:08:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再胡鬧了 由乃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.59,0:08:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不告訴我卡片藏在哪裡也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.04,0:08:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只聽一下我的預測好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.03,0:08:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 來得正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.71,0:08:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 能否把這個吵人傢伙帶出去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.08,0:08:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.41,0:08:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐是小氣鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.22,0:08:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.56,0:08:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳同學 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.98,0:09:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃同學 請稍等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.22,0:09:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.70,0:09:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.67,0:09:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 昨天真是對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.09,0:09:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 如果方便的話 今天能給我一點時間嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.78,0:09:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想繼續昨天的話題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.80,0:09:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.81,0:09:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋寶結束後如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.67,0:09:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我在溫室等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.53,0:09:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫室？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.18,0:09:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 那麼就在溫室見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.36,0:09:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝大家的勇躍參加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.73,0:09:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我說明一下活動規則
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.00,0:09:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要找的就是這些卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.85,0:09:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅 白 黃的卡片將分別藏在校內的某處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.14,0:09:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,限制時間是一小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.16,0:10:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到卡片後 請帶回到作為本部的薔薇館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.28,0:10:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著就可獲贈\N作為附加獎的與花蕾們的半天約會權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.06,0:10:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受歡迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.18,0:10:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.38,0:10:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 請花蕾的姐妹們到前面來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.70,0:10:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了公平起見 請花蕾的姐妹們遲五分鐘開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.11,0:10:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！ 怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.31,0:10:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 開始！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.88,0:10:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在活動結束前 花蕾們請來這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.65,0:10:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到黃薔薇大人竟然也會參加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.24,0:10:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒理由白白放過這麼有趣的活動吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.26,0:10:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 我一定會找到紅色的卡片的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.53,0:10:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 稍微招呼一下客人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.32,0:10:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 方便的話能否進來談談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.29,0:11:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有花蕾們在哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.76,0:11:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白薔薇大人不想去找志摩子同學的卡片嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.17,0:11:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你說是志摩子的卡片…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.86,0:11:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 關於隱藏的地點我是一點頭緒也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.82,0:11:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 明明志摩子同學的卡片大概就在那裡的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.78,0:11:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.60,0:11:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說那個房間裡藏著甚麼好東西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.39,0:11:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.75,0:11:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 已過了5分鐘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.81,0:11:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.05,0:11:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.52,0:11:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待著祐巳的英勇奮鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.74,0:11:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.46,0:11:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳同學 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.41,0:11:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.31,0:11:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕啊 志摩子同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.38,0:11:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以跟白薔薇大人約會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.88,0:11:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人既沒參加甚麼俱樂部活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.00,0:11:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒加入甚麼委員會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.41,0:12:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.17,0:12:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是在薔薇館裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.96,0:12:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.18,0:12:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.15,0:12:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.04,0:12:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是祥子大人的FAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.64,0:12:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概以為我知道卡片藏在哪裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.50,0:12:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.24,0:12:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～ 現在可不是玩捉迷藏的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.65,0:12:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～ 還有十五分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.05,0:12:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人的紅色卡片到底在哪裡呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.10,0:12:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我要藏的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.03,0:12:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.47,0:13:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我的話 一定會藏在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.41,0:13:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.77,0:13:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 好像嚇到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.00,0:13:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.56,0:13:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是來這裡找卡片嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.02,0:13:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.52,0:13:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人 比我更早來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.93,0:13:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 看起來還未找到卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.60,0:13:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.45,0:13:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.13,0:13:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想卡片應該就在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.52,0:13:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方便的話 請用這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.42,0:13:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.73,0:13:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那裡沒有卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.21,0:13:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.46,0:13:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我說晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.72,0:14:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上我剛才也挖掘過那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.56,0:14:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.26,0:14:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼會認為卡片在那裡呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.35,0:14:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.53,0:14:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這個薔薇就叫做紅薔薇啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.72,0:14:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經到4點40分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.00,0:14:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加活動的同學們請立刻到中庭集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.21,0:14:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 我們將發表本次活動的結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.86,0:14:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花蕾們的卡片有兩張被發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.43,0:14:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 沒找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.64,0:14:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為令不給我提示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.86,0:14:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.32,0:14:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐的卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.79,0:14:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以為一定會在那裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.97,0:14:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是找到白色卡片的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.66,0:14:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二年級藤組 蟹名靜同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.75,0:15:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～ 是靜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.39,0:15:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明用表情給過提示的 這個人真是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.70,0:15:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到白色卡片的地點是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.63,0:15:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委員會的公告牌上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.43,0:15:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 不在薔薇館的第一層嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.28,0:15:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼志摩子同學為甚麼那時會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.26,0:15:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著 是找到黃色卡片的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.66,0:15:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年級菊組 田沼千里同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.06,0:15:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地點是在圖書館裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.29,0:15:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圖書館我也去找過啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.97,0:15:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.10,0:15:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅薔薇的花蕾的卡片誰也沒發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.85,0:15:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也沒有？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.99,0:15:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅薔薇的花蕾 紅色卡片究竟在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.79,0:15:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 一起去收回卡片吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.90,0:15:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.49,0:16:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也來過這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.05,0:16:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 卻沒有找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.83,0:16:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找了哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.70,0:16:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在紅薔薇根莖的附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.19,0:16:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.53,0:16:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的找了這裡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.78,0:16:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.89,0:16:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.94,0:16:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.61,0:16:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明挖掘過同一個地方的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.86,0:16:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳同學 雖然很遺憾…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.66,0:16:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒說謊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.19,0:16:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有證人在場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.45,0:16:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.48,0:16:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是… 不認識的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.33,0:16:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就沒法成為證人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.01,0:16:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.91,0:16:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.34,0:16:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都說到這種地步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.70,0:16:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是真的不在吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.30,0:16:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.52,0:17:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 這張卡片放在了比我原來埋得更深的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.37,0:17:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.00,0:17:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.20,0:17:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖瓦倫丁做了一個惡作劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.64,0:17:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣去想不是很好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.13,0:17:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然紅薔薇的花蕾都這樣說了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.90,0:17:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.91,0:17:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 能在薔薇館等我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.17,0:17:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.70,0:17:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志摩子同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.22,0:17:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.51,0:17:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇哦 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.24,0:17:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我特意等在這裡為你送的巧克力說聲謝謝呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.01,0:17:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.48,0:18:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力的話這裡有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.27,0:18:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是非常難吃的夾心巧克力就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.98,0:18:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.22,0:18:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來 放在那裡的巧克力不是祐巳的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.28,0:18:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.31,0:18:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 我已經吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.30,0:18:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為祐巳緊盯著那扇門 所以我完全以為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.46,0:18:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是非常美味的大理石花紋蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.16,0:18:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過好像是初學者做的 樣子稍微有點變形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.31,0:18:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 那是粉紅色的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.94,0:18:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 粉紅色的包裝紙上印著白色薔薇花紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.25,0:18:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在薔薇館第一層裡藏的不是白色卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.75,0:18:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是志摩子同學因為猶豫著該不該交給\N白薔薇大人而一直放在那裡的巧克力蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.68,0:18:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也算聖瓦倫丁的一個惡作劇吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.95,0:19:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.14,0:19:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.64,0:19:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有東西希望你能收下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.47,0:19:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道… 不會是念珠吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.40,0:19:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,念珠！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.66,0:19:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.20,0:19:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.19,0:19:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我一年級的時候 好像是被姐姐完全看穿了似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.62,0:19:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我對你的心事卻不怎麼了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.95,0:19:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以漸漸變得沒有自信了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.39,0:19:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.77,0:19:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 看起來你好像在避開我 所以稍微有點急躁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.96,0:19:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那是我的誤解吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.37,0:19:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 那是因為我想把這個送給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.48,0:19:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在令大人的幫助下做出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.14,0:19:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為想先對姐姐保密 才會偷偷摸摸地去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.23,0:20:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人在那裡沾沾自喜地做得起勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.29,0:20:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻完全沒有想到姐姐會怎麼想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.40,0:20:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.03,0:20:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的 姐姐討厭情人節的巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.45,0:20:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我無論如何也想將\N平常那種感謝的心情化為有形的物質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.67,0:20:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.45,0:20:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.27,0:20:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過討厭甚麼的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.80,0:20:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所厭煩的只是一部份學生隨便地\N將送巧克力的慾望想放在我身上實現而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.41,0:20:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你為我做的東西的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.89,0:20:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然會很高興地收下它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.37,0:20:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能給我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.24,0:20:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.29,0:20:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了我不是討厭巧克力…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.36,0:20:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一個不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.79,0:20:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 請拿這邊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.51,0:20:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人請放手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.74,0:20:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳你才應該…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.64,0:21:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.17,0:21:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 又是在做甚麼表演嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.86,0:21:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是的 這叫做「吃驚的巧克力」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.92,0:21:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡面混入了難吃得讓人歪嘴的「不中」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.89,0:21:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才叫「吃驚」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.04,0:21:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.05,0:21:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.61,0:21:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.95,0:21:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.40,0:21:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼那就是「中」了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.17,0:21:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明「中」與「不中」都有一個不見了的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.10,0:21:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人會吃到「中」也算是聖瓦倫丁的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.77,0:21:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃到「中」會有甚麼好事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.66,0:22:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.68,0:22:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃到「中」的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.59,0:22:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會無一例外地獲贈與我的半天約會權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.97,0:23:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被不認識的某人偷偷地思念也是很浪漫的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.50,0:23:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到是喜歡清清楚楚、明明白白地去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.83,0:23:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想下一周的故事一定會讓人焦躁不安吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.40,0:23:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也會一邊發牢騷一邊看下去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.55,0:23:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話一點都不像姐姐 只是一個老姑婆而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.10,0:23:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！？
